name: Pad Thai
detail: It is typically made with rice noodles, shrimp, peanuts, a scrambled egg, and bean sprouts. The ingredients are fried in a wok.

name: Phat kaphrao
detail: pad kaprao is a combination of stir fried chilies, garlic, protein, and the most essential that distinguishes it from all other dishes.

name: Khao Soi
detail: Khao Soi is a deliciously creamy and slightly spicy yellow curry dish unique to Northern Thailand.

name: Tom Yum Goong
detail: Tom Yam is a type of soup with distinct sharp hot and sour flavors, scented with a pleasant citrusy aroma.

name: Chicken Green Curry
detail: This Thai curry has a beautifully fresh flavor thanks to a homemade curry paste and the addition of Thai basil, cilantro, and makrut lime leaf and peel.

name: Mango Sticky Rice
detail: Mango sticky rice is a traditional Southeast Asian and South Asian dessert made with glutinous rice, fresh mango and coconut milk.
